                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "q"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "-analogue of Gosper’s identity that is inequivalent to Yamaguchi’s "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "q"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "-analogue. We also show how a similar approach can be applied much more broadly in the construction of "
