        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "We thus obtain a q-analogue of the shifted factorial in the sense that limq→1 (qa;q)n(1−q) n "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "q"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "\\begin{array} { r } { \\operatorname* { l i m } _ { q \\to 1 } \\frac { ( q ^ { a } ; q ) _ { n } } { ( 1 - q ) ^ { n } } = ( a ) _ { n } } \\end{array}"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": ". Basic hypergeometric series of the form "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "{ } _ { r } \\phi _ { r - 1 }"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "may then be defined so that "
